intent: Count the total number of products on sale that are priced between $20 and $100.
query: SELECT COUNT(*) AS sale_product_count FROM catalog_product_index_price AS cpip JOIN salesrule_product_attribute AS srpa ON cpip.entity_id = srpa.rule_id WHERE cpip.final_price BETWEEN 20 AND 100 AND srpa.rule_id IN (SELECT rule_id FROM salesrule WHERE is_active = 1);
